---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<Layout title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`}>
	<main class="page-shell py-10 md:py-14">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
			<header class="mb-10">
				<p class="mb-1 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-zinc-400">About</p>
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">{SITE_TITLE}</h1>
			</header>

			<div class="markdown-prose">
				<p>
					Welcome to {SITE_TITLE}! This blog is a personal space for sharing research notes,
					engineering logs, and technical essays on software development, systems design,
					and technology.
				</p>

				<h2>About Me</h2>
				<p>
					I'm a software engineer passionate about building robust systems, writing clean code,
					and documenting the things I learn along the way. This blog serves as both a personal
					knowledge base and a way to give back to the developer community.
				</p>

				<h2>Topics</h2>
				<p>
					Posts on this blog cover a range of topics including:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Software Engineering & Architecture</li>
					<li>Web Development & DevOps</li>
					<li>Programming Languages & Tools</li>
					<li>Technical Problem Solving</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Contact</h2>
				<p>
					Feel free to reach out through GitHub or open an issue on the blog's repository
					if you have questions or suggestions.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
